Class Line

  • java.lang.Object
    • Line

  • public class Line
extends java.lang.Object
    Line.java: Class that stores properties for all of the lines. Includes x and y coordinates, as well as information used for operation of algorithm. Code released under GNU GPLv3.
    Author:
    Shane Christy
